I worked on a TikTok video production project for **Aeon Beta**, managed through **CleverAds** as the agency partner. The goal was to develop and produce **31 TikTok videos** to help build the channel presence of Aeon Beta’s newly opened cinema locations in **Hanoi and Hai Phong**. The project focused on creating a strong content foundation for launch, with videos designed to match the brand, attract attention, and support early channel growth.
